name: Qr05_Base_Fim_Plano_Ourocap_PU_PP_ComOTC_OTC290_NeoBpo
queryText:
SELECT
  '001'+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 9)+
  REPLICATE ('0' , 9)+
  '1'+
  RIGHT(REPLICATE ('0' , 15)+CONVERT(VARCHAR, CPF_CNPJ), 15)+
  CONVERT(VARCHAR(10), CONVERT(DATE, DT_NASCIMENTO, 103), 112)+
  LEFT(CONVERT(VARCHAR(60), NOME) + REPLICATE(' ', 60), 60)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 1)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 2)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 4)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 10)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 4)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 10)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 4)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 10)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 5)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 2)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 73)+
  REPLICATE (' ' , 70) AS BASE
FROM
  TB_BASE_FIM_PLANO_OUROCAP_PU_PP_COMOTC_NEOBPO_FILTRADA
